overview: On March 5th GCW presents Ransom live on FITE straight Showboat Hotel in Atlantic City, NJ. The event features the debut of The Motor City Machine Guns and the JCW Title Match where Jordan Oliver vs Blake Christian.  Also scheduled to appear: Mason vs Allie in a Steel Cage Match Los Macizos vs MCMG  Bailey vs Drew Parker Maki Itoh & Rina & Veny vs Sawyer & Billie & Janai  Masha Slamovich vs JWM Joey Janela vs Kirk +more!
title: GCW Ransom
